  "aiSummary": "# Universal Tuya Zigbee GitHub Activity Summary\n\n## New Device Requests\n- **Issue #1348**: Device request for an unspecified device with fingerprint `_TZ3210_xzhnra8x` (open). [Link](https://github.com/JohanBendz/com.tuya.zigbee/issues/1348)\n- **Issue #1331**: Device request for Moes UFO-R11 with new fingerprint `_TZ3290_ot6ewjvmej` (open). [Link](https://github.com/JohanBendz/com.tuya.zigbee/issues/1331)\n\n## Existing Fingerprints Supported\n- **Issue #110**: \n  - `_TZ3210_w0qqde0g` - Supported by `plug_energy_monitor`\n  - `_TZ3000_w0qqde0g` - Supported by `plug_energy_monitor`\n  - `_TZ3000_gjnozsaz` - Supported by `button_emergency_sos`, `plug_energy_monitor`\n  \n- **Issue #128**: \n  - `_TZE204_nklqjk62` - Supported by `garage_door`\n  \n- **Issue #135**: \n  - Multiple fingerprints for curtain motors and irrigation valves, including:\n    - `_TZE200_xlppj4f5` - Supported by `valve_irrigation`\n    - `_TZ3210_0jxeoadc` - Supported by `valve_irrigation`\n    - Various curtain motor fingerprints supporting `curtain_motor` and `curtain_motor_tilt`.\n\n## Fingerprints from Forks to Integrate\n- No new fingerprints from forks were identified in the current analysis.\n\n## Pull Requests with Useful Changes\n- **PR #125**: Fix for HOBEIAN 10G radar sensor, addressing IAS motion conflict and battery read issues. [Link](https://github.com/dlnraja/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/125)\n- **PR #118**: Support for fingerprint `_TZ3000_ysdv91bk`. [Link](https://github.com/dlnraja/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/118)\n- **PR #116**: Added support for Bseed 1-Gang Switch with physical button detection. [Link](https://github.com/dlnraja/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/116)\n- **PR #111**: Separate driver for Tuya/Bseed touch dimmer (merged). [Link](https://github.com/dlnraja/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/111)\n- **PR #106**: Added fingerprint `_TZE204_n9ctkb6j`, addressing case sensitivity (merged). [Link](https://github.com/dlnraja/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/106)\n- **PR #1210**: Addition of Garage Door Controller and combined Fan drivers. [Link](https://github.com/JohanBendz/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/1210)\n- **PR #1253**: Added three new devices. [Link](https://github.com/JohanBendz/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/1253)\n- **PR #1292**: Added radar and illuminance sensor. [Link](https://github.com/JohanBendz/com.tuya.zigbee/pull/1292)\n\nThis summary encapsulates the latest developments in the Universal Tuya Zigbee project, highlighting new device requests, existing fingerprint support, and significant pull requests that enhance functionality. For further details, please refer to the linked issues and pull requests."
